{"tid":1556254,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[推上國際] 九月十日球場大合唱，不畏恐怖主義，堅決捍衛民主","createTime":"2019-09-09T16:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T08:43:07.000Z","uid":105032,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d2eb0ea1271504b0046cd4767d9274f78550d3","tid":1556254,"uid":105032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:00:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">四年前英國球迷為法國獻唱馬賽曲，以紀念死去既無辜市民，決心對抗<span style=\"color: red;\">恐怖主義</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://amp.france24.com/en/20151117-wembley-stadium-erupts-with-french-national-anthem-after-paris-attacks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.france24.com%2Fen%2F20151117-wembley-stadium-erupts-with-french-national-anthem-after-paris-attacks&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=5904cb1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://amp.france24.com/en/20151117-wembley-stadium-erupts-with-french-national-anthem-after-paris-attacks</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>哩個係一個推上國際既機會！四年後既今日，我希望香港球迷不畏國家恐怖主義，為所有受到暴力摧殘既抗爭者唱出<span style=\"color: gold;\">願榮耀歸香港，</span>一首代表香港抗爭者既歌曲</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今次目標清晰明確，就係表達我地爭取民主自由、追求公義既決心，不畏恐怖主義，不向獨裁低頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">既然人鍊都咁成功，我希望哩次都成功<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"3f560d2e8845f2a276f063596efe13d24f155149","tid":1556254,"uid":105032,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:01:08.000Z","msg":"馬賽曲<br />\nAllons enfants de la Patrie,<br />\nLe jour de gloire est arriv&eacute; !<br />\nContre nous de la tyrannie,<br />\nL'&eacute;tendard sanglant est lev&eacute; (bis)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Entendez-vous dans les campagnes<br />\nMugir ces f&eacute;roces soldats ?<br />\nIls viennent jusque dans vos bras<br />\nEgorger vos fils,vos compagnes !</span><br />\nRefrain<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Aux armes, citoyens!<br />\nFormez vos bataillons!</span></span><br />\nMarchons, marchons !<br />\nQu'un sang impur<br />\nAbreuve nos sillons !<br />\n<br />\n一起走吧，祖國的子民們！<br />\n榮耀之日來臨了！<br />\n那暴政對着我們，<br />\n升起了染血的軍旗！(兩遍)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你們可聽到在鄉間<br />\n殘暴士兵們的吼叫？<br />\n他們會來到你們跟前<br />\n殘殺你們的孩子，你們的伴侶！</span><br />\n副歌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拿起武器，公民們，<br />\n排好你們的隊伍！</span></span><br />\n進軍，進軍！<br />\n讓不潔之血<br />\n灌溉我們的壕溝！"},{"pid":"4991a04864b6dfa2f4cba947d97dcc1613203e6e","tid":1556254,"uid":2904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[全民和你唱]</span></span> 全世界全天候街邊唱香港國歌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556100</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cde54af3aa482f36423548cdecb8a6abd58c55bd","tid":1556254,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9ef47ce0c4d0e42d7ba52898264d1134bd9229","tid":1556254,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"點解無人理hkfp果個auntie架...會死人架..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1555740/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1555740/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"4d4f478f6a03617ac87fd420166e97754c40b1c6","tid":1556254,"uid":105032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b9ef47ce0c4d0e42d7ba52898264d1134bd9229","tid":1556254,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"點解無人理hkfp果個auntie架...會死人架..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n