e":"2019-09-09T16:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9925bc5eb5ebc461bf17aef6572bf5c0137e09","tid":1556254,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:21:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5b9c14e7736283c0ca3bdc0813072d789e46da6a","tid":1556254,"uid":105032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffc4c5d7ec75a6dc2b60a3834c7cf96e3041001","tid":1556254,"uid":105032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}